ZH: 他们低估了我在公司的价值。
EN: They underestimated my value in the company.

ZH: 这种疾病不能低估，必须及时治疗。
EN: This illness should not be underestimated, it must be treated promptly.

ZH: 我们不能低估这场比赛的难度。
EN: We cannot underestimate the difficulty of this game.

